dct_description_sm: Survey of India. Relief shown by 5 ft and 10 ft contour intervals and spot heights. Surveyed 1956-57. Published under the authority of Brigadier Gambhir Singh, Surveyor General of India. Map Library does not have the all the sheets to complete this set.
